GamePlay:
--------- 
 Your mission is avoid to collide with yourself, walls or opponent and
 make your opponent to collide.

System requirements:
--------------------
 Works on all 1 meg Amigas (except Amiga 1000).


Files:
------
 FILE_ID.DIZ   BBS information
 SuperT.doc    Documentation.
 SuperT.exe    Main program file, run this to play.
 SuperT.Readme Aminet information.

Ingame Keys:
 ESC -  Quit Round

Controlling The Players:

 Key Setup1:
	Left  - LeftArrow
	Right - RightArrow
	Up    - Arrow up
	Down  - Arrow down

Key Setup2:
	Left  - A
	Right - S
	Up    - D
	Down  - X

