S.O.S
-----
 Software Of Sweden is an old demo group. It was formed in 1986 by Ron
 (Spectrum & C64) and SAL (C64). In 1987 S.O.S Where amongst the greatest
 on the Swedish Amiga demo scene. In 1995 we started to work on the PC.
 Right now we are only two active members: Ron and Beast.


Development:
------------
 Super Tron 97 Amiga is written in assembler by
 Ronny Nordqvist (Ron/S.O.S).

 Super Tron 97 PC is written in pascal and assembler by
 Christian Bjorkqvist (Beast/S.O.S).

 Thanx to JCH for PC-music routine :) .

